POST http://localhost:8080/agent/investigate
Content-Type: text/plain

You MUST call these tools in this exact order:

STEP 1: Call getCustomerDetails with customerId="CUST-001"
STEP 2: Call analyzeTransaction with these exact values:
        transactionId="TXN-AGENT-001"
        customerId="CUST-001"
        amount=4500
        merchantName="Unknown Electronics"
        merchantCategory="Electronics"
        transactionLocation="Lagos Nigeria"
        customerHomeLocation="Dallas Texas"
        customerAverageSpend=150
        isInternational=true
        timestamp="3AM"
STEP 3: Call addToReviewQueue with findings from STEP 2
STEP 4: Report what you did